  "keyFeatures": [
    "Strongly-typed Entity and Aggregate Root base classes with built-in domain event support",
    "Value Object base class with structural equality and comparison",
    "Event-sourced aggregate roots via BaseEventSourcedAggregateRoot with replay from history",
    "CQRS command and query buses backed by MediatR",
    "Pre-built MediatR pipeline behaviors: validation, authorization, caching, logging, performance tracking, unit of work",
    "Integration event and command buses using MassTransit over RabbitMQ",
    "Entity Framework Core base repositories with auditing, soft-delete, and outbox pattern support",
    "KurrentDB (EventStoreDB) integration for event-sourced aggregates with catch-up and persistent subscriptions",
    "Hybrid cache service abstraction for transparent caching/invalidation in queries",
    "HTTP REST API presentation helpers: BaseApiCommandController, BaseApiQueryController, ExceptionMiddleware, ProblemDetails response builder"
  ],
